# library trio.  The axis anchors on a single pure-host-language async
# QUIC stack with TLS 1.3 integration, stream multiplexing, congestion
# control (Cubic + BBR), loss recovery, ECN, RFC 9221 unreliable
# datagrams, and an embedding API suitable for both server-accept and
# client-connect roles:
#
#     Rust    : quinn                      by Quinn org (Dirkjan
#                                              Ochtman + Benjamin
#                                              Saunders + Ralith);
#                                              pure-Rust async-first
#                                              IETF QUIC v1
#                                              implementation.
