# Cycle position in current 3+1 micro-cycle:
#   Rust=247     ← THIS FILE          (axis 192 OPENS, slot 1/0/0)
#   Go=247       ← next round         (axis 192 continues, slot 2/0/0)
#   TS-Node=247  ← round after        (axis 192 CLOSES at triple-247, 1/1/1)
